Adjusting Image Contrast

I = imread("img/IMG_001.jpg");
I2 = imread("img/IMG_002.jpg");
gs = im2gray(I);
gs2 = im2gray(I2);
imshowpair(gs,gs2,"montage")
histogram
imhist(gs)
imhist(gs2)
range gs2 gs
matlab function brighten brighter pixels and darkens darker pixels
gs2Adj = imadjust(gs2);
imhist(gs2Adj)
histogram ( histogram equalization)
imshowpair(gs2, gs2Adj, "montage")
imadjust() imlocalbrighten()
I2adj = imlocalbrighten(I2);
imshowpair(I2, I2adj, "montage")
